{"tid":2109191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林朗彥被控去年3月15日政總襲擊保安 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-07-15T05:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T08:38:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b19dc9ed28f16ff5a8890a4b2a07c275722a54ae","tid":2109191,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F6974&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=6a8fde58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6974</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭  <br />\n#何俊堯裁判官<br />\n#0315金鐘 #審訊<br />\n<br />\n👤林朗彥 (眾志主席)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：普通襲擊<br />\n被控於2019年3月15日，在添馬添美道2號政府總部東翼地下公眾入口大堂內，襲擊男子梁炳森。<br />\n<br />\n內容後補<br />\n<br />\n🎊罪名不成立🎊"},{"pid":"a9d3b4c315a4ba227f9696c8d92fe08c7cbf65a2","tid":2109191,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868d81f60115aa66007109acdff6fed2467d1008","tid":2109191,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73ba385f0253ad2f1492d5239dfcfe2f40bd5ac","tid":2109191,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"何官就嚟俾人告國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea170a63a59ae692e66d9bac69fe56e5cda335d","tid":2109191,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"等睇律政狗咬實上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2571cc03fa951add78a10fe0f92e82f2c8b5ef95","tid":2109191,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e73ba385f0253ad2f1492d5239dfcfe2f40bd5ac","tid":210919