\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178ec5296c303ab93dd340556f3fab767486c482","tid":2109191,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2571cc03fa951add78a10fe0f92e82f2c8b5ef95","tid":2109191,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e73ba385f0253ad2f1492d5239dfcfe2f40bd5ac","tid":2109191,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"何官就嚟俾人告國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"佢只係做本份用法律原則去睇啲證據口供嚟審案 但單係咁做已經要日日提心吊膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"This is hk <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab46baab7f5ccf1850a76f1dd096b2aafb00c3e","tid":2109191,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3c4578d93b96dc18ba5a5e5f556d61a9966288","tid":2109191,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea170a63a59ae692e66d9bac69fe56e5cda335d","tid":2109191,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"等睇律政狗咬實上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"除非有新証據或原則性錯誤 唔係唔可以上訴"},{"pid":"7b1247e918abee9014d0ec55574830700c1e29c2","tid":2109191,"uid":362935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6baf4d5068a56ca736a0b461e250d3d1954572d0","tid":2109191,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd3c4578d93b96dc18ba5a5e5f556d61a9966288","tid":2109191,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea170a63a59ae692e66d9bac69fe56e5cda335d","tid":2109191,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"等睇律政狗咬實上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"除非有新証據或原則性錯誤 唔係唔可以上訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"我知<br />\n冇都講到有㗎啦<br />\n最多咪駁回上訴申請<br />\n佢又冇成本"},{"pid":"aa7400ada796dcb308de79e8be60ba041aed6ded","tid":2109191,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">梁炳森在庭上供稱，事發當日早上，他獲上司告知政總將有示威。當值期間他見到被告衝入大堂，似乎想越過他身後的閘機。他於是捉住被告的背囊阻止。未料被告撞向他，二人雙雙跌倒。當時他背部著地，遭被告壓住心口，右邊臀部被褲袋裡的電話壓到，感到痛楚。<br />\n<br />\n案件裁定表證成立後，被告選擇不作供，案件僅半日便審結。何俊堯裁判官裁決時指出，事主的證供與現場閉路電視有很大分別。根據閉路電視，當時乃事主主動上前攔截被告，「睇唔到被告有撞向佢」。而二人跌倒時，更是事主趴在地上壓住被告。當時事主的臀部沒有著地，故沒有可能會被電話壓到。加上事主亦承認對事件細節的記憶模糊，故其證供令人不能放心依賴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，由於閉路電視拍攝不到事發時的細節，例如被告及事主如何跌倒、事主為何會壓住被告等。基於疑點利益歸於被告，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n散庭後，林朗彥在庭外表示，是次脫罪很大原因在於保安的不誠實，他又籲政總保安或執法人員，不要為入罪而扭曲事實。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4d1979d6708228a5843ce0b496a8941902875232","tid":2109191,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"香港定唔定罪已經唔係睇証據<br />\n睇運"},{"pid":"51ba6c60c5cd3aa27dfc9b78dd276d8ee3b9de16","tid":2109191,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d1979d6708228a5843ce0b496a8941902875232","tid":2109191,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"香港定唔定罪已經唔係睇証據<br />\n睇運"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162a5fd8b0a5c009e915af316040ef342ae95dfc","